name: i want my money back
description:
you just started at community college, leaving behind everything you've ever cared about. make friends, skip class, get lost in the multiverse.

this game is based off a story i started in 2013 as a sad & poor freshman, left unfinished in 2015, and finally turned into a game as a strong, confident, still poor graduate student. 

cw: lots of vulgar language. some of the colors can be hard to read on certain screens. i'm sorry!
